<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-565] Features incorrectly hashed in Minhash</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-565</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Given a feature vector for which minhash signature is desired, each feature id (an integer) is converted to a byte array through a series of bit shift operations. Current implementation of these operations doesn&apos;t mask the bits being shifted resulting in sign bit being shifted.   &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12493409">MAHOUT-565</key>
            <summary>Features incorrectly hashed in Minhash</summary>
